history.description: Specifies that friendly troopers with a faceup order token do not benefit from backup.
Instead of performing 1 additional attack, he may perform an additional attack action even if he already attacked during his activation.

Lost Scout keyword. Doesn't have to deploy at the end of setup.
Now gives 2 suppression by default and an additional suppression on rounds 4 and 5 instead of 5 and 6.

Changed to whenever Vader is attacked instead of on Deflect. No longer gives a dodge.
Removed Fire Support keyword, instead 3 red dice are added to friendly attacks within range 2 of Rex.
Lost Reliable 1 and gained Inspire 1 keywords. No longer gives her a dodge. Now divulged during resolve setup effects step rather than deploy units step.
Can be placed in friendly territory. Cad bane cannoy deploy or perform actions until the token is revealed.

No longer surges to hit. Gained Critical 3 keyword.
